name: Studio Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Studio Eye to your character in-game. Only a Ralien Studio member can get this item

name: Special Reward Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Special Reward Eye to your character in-game. Only someone who has helped with the development of Drone Wars in Special way, can get this item

name: Alpha Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Alpha Eye to your drone in-game. Only players who have participated in Closed testing sessions for Drone Wars can get this item

name: Premium Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Premium Eye to your character in-game. This item comes with the Drone Wars Peremium edition

name: YouTube Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic YouTube Eye to your character in-game. Only YouTubers who have created a few Drone Wars videos, or/and helped with with getting Drone Wars more players, can get this skin.

name: Twitch Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Twitch Eye to your character in-game. Only Streamers who have streamed Drone Wars a few times, or/and helped with with getting Drone Wars more players, can get this skin.

name: Experienced Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Experienced Eye to your character in-game. Only Players who have played Drone Wars at least 100 hours can get this item.

name: Pro Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Experienced Eye to your character in-game. Only Players who have played Drone Wars at least 1000 hours can get this skin.

name: Tournament Master Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Tournament Master Eye to your character in-game. Only Players who have won an official Drone Wars Tournament, can get this item.

name: Developer Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Developer eye to your character in-game. Only a Drone Wars Developer can get this item

name: Mystery Chest
description: Mystery Chest, that can be opened with a mystery key, and unlock one random item of multiple items inside the mystery Chest. This item can be granted via in-game item drops.

name: Mystery Gift
description: Mystery Gift, that can be opened without any key, and unlock one random item of multiple items inside the mystery gift. This item can be granted via in-game item drops, but only during special events, like eg. Christmas, Easter or special game events

name: Mystery Key
description: Mystery Key, can be used to open one 'Mystery Chests'

name: Early Access Eye
description: Special item. When equipped, this applies the cosmetic Early Access Eye to your character in-game. Only players that played Drone Wars during the Early Access phase, can get this item.

name: Turbine Engines ST 1
description: Special Engines. When equipped, this applies the Turbine Engines ST 1 to your character in-game.
